;LMW human uPA/A145 was concentrated to 10 mg/ml and 
incubated in 50 mM HEPES, 5.0 mM NaCl. pH 7.0, 1.4 mM 
4-iodobenzo[b]thiophene-2-carboxamidine for 15 min on ice.
The complex was crystallized by vapor diffusion in hanging drops containing 
equal volumes of protein-inhibitor solution (0.28 mM uPA/A145, 1.4 mM
inhibitor) and well solution (20 % 2-propanol, 20 % PEG 4K, 
100 mM sodium citrate, pH 6.5) sealed over the well.
;
